  "texts": [
    "Note as well how the proper noun 'Sarah' is translated as 'Laura'.",
    "EN \"And when Elliot was first born, we <A1> took her to the pediatrician <A2> and we met our first nurse <F> -we'll call her Sarah.\"",
    "IT \"E quando Elliot è nata per la prima volta, l'abbiamo portata dal pediatra e abbiamo incontrato la nostra prima infermierala chiameremo Laura.\"",
